"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/487126","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2016-04-11","<p>The information requested is not currently available. During 2016 we will be publishing further statistics on Universal Credit which will be published in accordance with the relevant protocols in the Code of Practice for Official Statistics.</p>","Witham","Priti Patel",,"2016-04-11T11:00:20.527Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/487126/answer","Biography information for Priti Patel","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/487126/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/487126/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2016-03-24","Universal Credit: EU Nationals","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, how many people from other EU member states were in receipt of universal credit in the most recent period for which figures are available; and what the cost to the public purse was of those payments of that credit.","false","Biography information for Anne-Marie Trevelyan","Berwick-upon-Tweed","Mrs Anne-Marie Trevelyan","32545"
